{
  "stem": "4284.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "As it turns out, I had to go through two evening selections with one Mengele, and the other one somebody else who was always interested in, in youngsters for experiments.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "The camp I was in in Auschwitz was famous for medical experiments because he was there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "There were experiments done for high altitude flying, for people freezing, all kinds of things.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Fortunately, none of us 131 was chosen for any of these experiments.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And, interestingly enough, every one of the 131 passed both inspections.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "I don't know if he was favorably inclined towards younger people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "We, we don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "Maybe he tried to save us for some other things.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "But we were not selected.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "My good fortune, so to speak, of speaking German make me stand out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And they make me a runner.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "A runner was from the stables with some documentation that we have a full head count, whatever it is.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "I have no idea what the-- going to the German administration.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And the one time that I had a-- the only kindness I was ever shown, I had to pass the camp bakery, which was, of course, being manned by inmates.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And they saw me walking by, and kind of surreptitiously, dropped a loaf of bread, which I proceeded to scoot up there and steal.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "Unfortunately, I got caught.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "The, the man in charge of the bakery caught me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "They yank me in and proceeded to beat the living daylights out of me till I finally said something in German.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And suddenly, having stopped the beating, he wasn't quite sure what to do.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was bleeding a little bit.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It wasn't the worst beating one could have.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it was sufficient for-- it's a good beginning, as far as he was concerned, to teach a lesson.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
